    "subtype": "siege_weapon",
    "text": "A tar spitter is a mass of tubes, pumps, and a copper tank mounted on an armored wagon. The tank is filled with hot tar under high pressure that can be sprayed from an aimed nozzle. The weaponized adhesive often roots enemies to the spot, making them easier prey for allied soldiers. Cleaning a tar spitter is a difficult task, and crew members usually wear thick leather aprons and gloves to avoid getting the tar on their skin.",
